.","searchKeywords":["zechora","daughter","nerias","rama","and","did","that","which","was","evil","the","sight","lord","according","all","his","fathers","revolted","from","him"]},{"verseId":"brenton_2-chronicles_36_8","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":14,"bookName":"2 Chronicles","bookAbbrev":"2-chronicles","chapter":36,"verse":8,"text":"not these things written in the book of the chronicles of the kings of Juda? And Joakim slept with his fathers, and was buried with his fathers in Ganozae: and Jechonias his son reigned in his stead.","searchKeywords":["not","these","things","written","the","book","chronicles","kings","juda","and","joakim","slept","with","his","fathers","was","buried","ganozae","jechonias","son","reigned","stead"]},{"verseId":"brenton_2-chronicles_36_9","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":14,"bookName":"2 Chronicles","bookAbbrev":"2-chronicles","chapter":36,"verse":9,"text":"eight years old when he began to reign, and he reigned three months and ten days in Jerusalem, and did that which was evil in the sight of the Lord.","searchKeywords":["eight","years","old","when","began","reign","and","reigned","three","months","ten","days","jerusalem","did","that","which","was","evil","the","sight","lord"]},{"verseId":"brenton_2-chronicles_36_11","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":14,"bookName":"2 Chronicles","bookAbbrev":"2-chronicles","chapter":36,"verse":11,"text":"twenty-one years old when he began to reign, and he reigned eleven years in Jerusalem.","searchKeywords":["twenty","one","years","old","when","began","reign","and","reigned","eleven","jerusalem"]},{"verseId":"brenton_2-chronicles_36_13","translationId":"brenton","testament":"OT","bookIndex":14,"bookName":"2 Chronicles","bookAbbrev":"2-chronicles","chapter":36,"verse":13,"text":": but he stiffened his neck, and hardened his heart, so as not to return to the Lord God of Israel.","searchKeywords":["but","stiffened","his","neck","and","harde